                  built with Node.js and MongoDB, enables institute students to
                  log in using their institute email IDs and complete an ID card
                  request form.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Administrators or authorized personnel can then review and
                  approve or reject these requests, streamlining the ID card
                  generation process. This automation significantly boosts
                  efficiency and accuracy, replacing manual labor.
                </p>
                <p>
                  This application processes around 500 ID card requests
                  annually, benefiting the Indian Institute of Information
                  Technology Guwahati.
